{"tid":2294790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李慧琼議助涉派禮誘投鄭泳舜","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T09:40:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a56f6417f93327306851da8b0ec1de9e1f8a9f","tid":2294790,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/R5LUNDBYINF2RNMRQI25TINUJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FR5LUNDBYINF2RNMRQI25TINUJI%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3yEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=eaddaa43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FR5LUNDBYINF2RNMRQI25TINUJI%2F&h=78617d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/R5LUNDBYINF2RNMRQI25TINUJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼議助涉派禮誘投鄭泳舜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kWR2bA7VFr7DPITJMf0ocptlkwU=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/24TWXUAWH5G4HJAJBZJKCWPDWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkWR2bA7VFr7DPITJMf0ocptlkwU%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F24TWXUAWH5G4HJAJBZJKCWPDWY.jpg&h=8a80923b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告陳惠娟（左圖）及李謀（右圖）未收到涉案福袋已被捕。<br />\n<br />\n【2018九西補選】【本報訊】民建聯立法會議員李慧琼議員辦事處兼職助理涉在2018年九龍西立法會補選中，與另一名居民組織女義工派發內含食物及日用品、價值百元的福袋予兩名深水埗海麗邨居民，誘使兩人投票給民建聯候選人鄭泳舜，惟福袋尚未交收，眾人已被捕。涉案四人昨就三項選舉舞弊控罪受審。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3E6DTrHA1eGdacYNOyMRr6FQBQg=/1233x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TZQNZBXGNRGKZJHA2B4HQXURJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3E6DTrHA1eGdacYNOyMRr6FQBQg%3D%2F1233x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTZQNZBXGNRGKZJHA2B4HQXURJI.jpg&h=47df66f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭泳舜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居民組織義工疑助登記<br />\n<br />\n三女一男被告包括王維霞（52歲）、「海麗之友社」義工鄧奕梅（42歲）、居民主婦陳惠娟（50歲）及無業男子李謀（50歲）。王事發時受聘於李慧琼議員辦事處，擔任兼職議員助理。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC3866/19"},{"pid":"483c118e9a46a47282842006087115e51298b674","tid":2294790,"uid":20317,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e799cf1685de254944a171001adc3f2fa098d2c","tid":2294790,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"李慧琼稍後會獲頒大紫驚表揚"}]}